      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "PACIFIC WARLORD (5) finds it hard to win with four victories from 42 starts. Did a good job last start to finish second over 1020m at this track, beaten half a length. In the right race and there is no reason he cannot get the major prize. PANTONG (3) is racing well and is close to a win, the latest effort a solid third at this track over 1020m. Consistent gelding but doesn't win often although this looks a nice race for him. DEFEATER (2) has put together back-to-back placings, the latest when one length away in second over 1200m at this track when he was prominent throughout. Nicely placed to find winning ways. DREAM MA (9) improved out of sight last start at the second run back, scoring by half a length over 1200m at this track. Has his share of talent. Hard to beat again in this suitable race.",
